Check whether a REDCap database has repeat forms

Source: R/utils.R
db_has_repeat_forms.Rd

Simple utility function checking for the existence of repeat forms in a REDCap database.

Usage

db_has_repeat_forms(db_data)

Arguments

db_data

A REDCap dataframe.

Value

A boolean.
